Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reagan being Reagan again
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wzvb
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 20 Mar 1983
Economic recovery sees Reagan shift his rhetoric back to the right-wing after 'Let Reagan be Reagan' calls. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less